                </div>
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <strong>Database Engineering</strong>
                    Schema design, indexing, upsert patterns, SQLite
                </div>
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <strong>CI/CD Implementation</strong>
                    GitHub Actions, automated testing, cross-platform validation
                </div>
